OL,4,CAbuse helpline takes hundreds of calls,
OL,5,Csays NSPCC
OL,6, A helpline launched for victims to
OL,7, report abuse and harassment in
OL,8, educational settings has taken hundreds
OL,9, of calls since it opened on 1 April.
OL,11,FThe service was set up by the
OL,12,FDepartment for Education after
OL,13,Ftestimonies alleging abuse were posted
OL,14,Fon the website Everyone's Invited.
OL,16,FThe helpline has had 353 calls and has
OL,17,Fmade 65 referrals to agencies such as
OL,18,Fthe police or children's services.
OL,20,FIt is is being run by the children's
OL,21,Fcharity the NSPCC.
